---
title: Sausage Risotto-Style Couscous with Peas and Roasted Cauliflower
description: We've swapped out traditional arborio rice in this risotto for a 35 min cheat! Sausage and Italian Spice-roasted cauliflower pack this hearty autumn dinner full of flavour. Enjoy!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/sausage-risotto-style-couscous-962141cb.jpg
